{"word":"ὑπορχέομαι","slug":"ὑπορχέομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑπορχέομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσομαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to dance with</i> or <i>to music</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> cogn., <el>ὄρχησιν ὑπ.</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to sing and dance</i> a character, of a pantomimic actor, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}